-- Polo Ralph Lauren forms group to develop new brands
-- 
-- Mon Jan 8, 2007 7:18am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/08/businesspro-poloralphlauren-dc-idUSWEN190320070108

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Polo Ralph Lauren Corp. ( RL.N ) is 
starting a new group, Global Brand Concepts, that will develop 
new lifestyle brands for specialty and department stores, the 
company said on Monday. 

  The group will be available to design, market and advertise 
clothes for men, women and children, as well as home products 
and accessories, it said.